    dc:date "2004" ;
    dc:title "A phylogenetic analysis of the Mimagathidini with revisionary notes on the genus Stantonia Ashmead, 1904 (Hymenoptera: Braconidae: Orgilinae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4675823>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4675891>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4675853>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4675855> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4675823>
    dc:description "FIGS 35–40. (35) Stantonia ngilima n. sp., paratype, ”. (36) S. procera, holotype, ”. (37) S. baiteta n. sp., holotype, ”. (38) S. seyrigi, holotype, ” (39) S. rossa n. sp., holotype, ”. (40) S. maracapatana n. sp., holotype, „. Mesosoma in lateral view (35, 36); propodeum (37–40) and anterior part of metasoma (37, 38)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4675823/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4675891>
    dc:description "FIGS 131–136. (131) Stantonia caudatus (Granger), holotype, ”. (132) S. baiteta sp. n., holotype, ”. (133, 135) S. rufithorax End., holotype, „. (134) S. sampaioi sp. n., holotype, „. (136) S. procera, holotype, ”. Lateral view of mesosoma (131, 132); dorsal view of propodeum (133, 134) and beginning of metasoma (133); detail of eyes (135); detail of apex of hind tibia (136)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4675891/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4675853>
    dc:description "FIGS 65–70. (65) Stantonia mazatlanensis n. sp., holotype, ”. (66, 67) S. pachycornis n. sp., „. (68–70) S. baiteta n. sp., holotype, ”. Head in lateral (65, 66) and dorsal view (70); mesosoma in lateral view (67, 68); first tergite in lateral view (69)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4675853/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4675855>
    dc:description "FIGS 71–76. (71) Stantonia baiteta n. sp., holotype, ”. (72–74) S. rossa n. sp., holotype, ”. (75, 76) S. bakeri n. sp., holotype, ”. Head in lateral view (71, 72); mesosoma in lateral view (73, 75); first tergite in lateral view (74, 76)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4675855/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

